[02:53.55]	We are two lions litter'd in one day,
[02:56.81]	And I the elder and more terrible:
[02:59.83]	And Caesar shall go forth.
[03:02.26]CALPURNIA	Alas, my lord,
[03:03.70]	Your wisdom is consumed in confidence.
[03:07.03]	Do not go forth to-day: call it my fear
